  "texts": [
    "Here, we characterize optimal methods, including the role of synthetic clinical text, for SDoH extraction using large language models.",
    "Specifically, we develop models to extract six key SDoH: employment status, housing issues, transportation issues, parental status, and social support.",
    "We investigate the value of incorporating large LM-generated synthetic SDoH data during the finetuning stage.",
    "We assess the performance of large LMs, including GPT3.5 and GPT4, in zero-and few-shot settings for identifying SDoH, and we explore the potential for algorithmic bias in LM predictions.",
    "Our methods could yield real-world evidence on SDoH, assist in identifying patients who could benefit from resource and social work support, and draw attention to the under-documented impact of social factors on health outcomes."
  ],
